QUEEN ELIZABETH'S GHOST
----------------------------------------------------------------------

    The thing about ghosts is that they are unpredictable. They turn
    up when you least expect them and then they scare the living
    daylights out of you. That's how they work. You cannot set your
    watch by a ghost because ghosts do not keep to schedules or time
    tables... apart from the ghost of Queen Elizabeth 1st which is
    supposed to make an annual appearance every March 24th in the
    courtyard of Richmond Palace.

